      • normalizeVersion

        public static String normalizeVersion(String version)
        Getting the normalized version of an artifact. The artifact has to have at least three digits inside the version separated by dots. If there are less than two dots inside the version it is extended with the necessary numbers of ".0".
        Parameters:
        version - The version that is checked.
        Returns:
        A normalizad version.

      • subFolderFile

        public static File subFolderFile(File parent,
                                 String... folderNames)
        Creates the file instance of a sub-folder.
        Parameters:
        parent - The parent folder that the folder structure is relative to.
        folderNames - The names of the sub-folders. The first one is the one that is the direct sub-folder of the parent folder, and the following sub folders are always the direct sub-folders of the previous ones.
        Returns:
        The file instance of the sub-folder.
